<CATEGORY> usa </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE>  Tornado Leaves Areas in Ruins </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WICHITA, Kan. (AP) -- The sun was shining and the wind was  
picking up Tuesday over Lake Shore Mobile Home Park, where a small, 
manmade lake was brimming with the remnants of people's lives. 
