<HEADLINE> Boston U. To Sell Three TV Stations </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	BOSTON (AP) -- Boston University announced Tuesday it will sell  
its three New England television stations to DP Media of Boston 
Inc. 
</P>
<P>
	The deal involves WABU of Boston, WZBU of Vineyard Haven, Mass.,  
and WNBU of Concord, N.H. 
</P>
<P>
	DP Media is affiliated with Pax TV and will broadcast the  
network's family-oriented programming. 
</P>
