	The three stations had broadcast the same programming, including  
Boston Red Sox games, Boston Celtics games, and locally produced 
shows like ``Business World,'' ``Doctors on Call,'' and ``Ch. 68 
Sports Night.'' 
</P>
<P>
	Financial terms of the deal, which will require regulatory  
approval, were not immediately released. 
</P>
<P>
	The school said the stations would continue to provide student  
internships and carry some university programming, including BU 
hockey. 
</P>
